sql: SELECT SUM(EMP_NUM), COUNT(DISTINCT EMP_LNAME), EMP_INITIAL FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR EMP_FNAME < (SELECT AVG(EMP_FNAME) FROM EMPLOYEE AS c WHERE c.EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 9)
SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM ENROLL WHERE  STU_NUM <= 54 LIMIT 10

SELECT PROF_NUM, CLASS_TIME FROM CLASS JOIN ENROLL JOIN COURSE ON CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE AND COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE WHERE CLASS_CODE NOT IN (SELECT CLASS_CODE FROM CLASS AS t WHERE  t.PROF_NUM >= 28) GROUP BY CLASS_TIME HAVING MIN(PROF_NUM) >= 32
SELECT CRS_CREDIT, CRS_DESCRIPTION FROM COURSE WHERE  CRS_CREDIT = 41 GROUP BY CRS_DESCRIPTION LIMIT 8
SELECT AVG(PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM) FROM EMPLOYEE JOIN PROFESSOR ON EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM = PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM WHERE EMP_DOB <= (SELECT MIN(EMP_DOB) FROM EMPLOYEE) LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT STU_NUM), PROF_NUM, STU_NUM FROM STUDENT JOIN DEPARTMENT ON DEPARTMENT.DEPT_CODE = STUDENT.DEPT_CODE WHERE  PROF_NUM <= 1 AND STU_FNAME NOT IN (SELECT STU_FNAME FROM STUDENT AS r WHERE r.STU_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  r.STU_NUM <= 49)
SELECT SUM(CRS_CREDIT), COUNT(DISTINCT CRS_CODE), CRS_DESCRIPTION FROM COURSE WHERE CRS_CREDIT BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  CRS_CREDIT <= 76 GROUP BY CRS_DESCRIPTION ORDER BY CRS_DESCRIPTION DESC LIMIT 5

SELECT CLASS.CRS_CODE, PROF_NUM FROM CLASS JOIN ENROLL JOIN COURSE ON CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE AND COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE WHERE EXISTS (SELECT * FROM COURSE AS b WHERE  b.CRS_CREDIT != 6 AND CLASS.CLASS_CODE = b.CRS_CODE LIMIT 9) GROUP BY PROF_NUM HAVING AVG(STU_NUM) < 94 ORDER BY PROF_NUM DESC
SELECT EMP_JOBCODE FROM EMPLOYEE JOIN CLASS ON CLASS.PROF_NUM = EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM WHERE EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  EMP_NUM != 82

SELECT AVG(STU_GPA) FROM STUDENT JOIN CLASS JOIN DEPARTMENT JOIN ENROLL ON DEPARTMENT.DEPT_CODE = STUDENT.DEPT_CODE AND CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE AND ENROLL.STU_NUM = STUDENT.STU_NUM WHERE  CLASS.PROF_NUM != 34 LIMIT 3
SELECT SUM(STU_GPA), DEPT_CODE FROM STUDENT WHERE STU_HRS BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR STU_HRS != (SELECT SUM(STU_HRS) FROM STUDENT AS t WHERE t.STU_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10) ORDER BY DEPT_CODE DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT DEPARTMENT.DEPT_NAME), b.EMP_NUM, b.EMP_NUM FROM DEPARTMENT AS b JOIN DEPARTMENT ON DEPARTMENT.DEPT_CODE = b.DEPT_CODE WHERE b.EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT CRS_CODE FROM CLASS WHERE PROF_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR CLASS_ROOM < (SELECT AVG(CLASS_ROOM) FROM CLASS LIMIT 7) ORDER BY CRS_CODE ASC
SELECT z.EMP_FNAME FROM EMPLOYEE AS z ORDER BY z.EMP_FNAME DESC
SELECT STU_HRS, STU_LNAME FROM STUDENT JOIN ENROLL ON ENROLL.STU_NUM = STUDENT.STU_NUM WHERE  ENROLL.STU_NUM >= 69
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT EMP_FNAME), COUNT(DISTINCT EMP_NUM), EMP_NUM, EMP_DOB FROM EMPLOYEE JOIN CLASS ON CLASS.PROF_NUM = EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM GROUP BY EMP_DOB HAVING SUM(EMP_NUM) = 37 LIMIT 4

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT STU_NUM), PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM FROM PROFESSOR JOIN EMPLOYEE JOIN CLASS JOIN ENROLL ON CLASS.PROF_NUM = EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM AND CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM = PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM WHERE DEPT_CODE <= (SELECT MIN(DEPT_CODE) FROM DEPARTMENT AS m WHERE  m.EMP_NUM >= 44 LIMIT 7)
SELECT ENROLL.STU_NUM, STU_CLASS FROM STUDENT JOIN DEPARTMENT JOIN ENROLL ON DEPARTMENT.DEPT_CODE = STUDENT.DEPT_CODE AND ENROLL.STU_NUM = STUDENT.STU_NUM WHERE  PROF_NUM <= 10 ORDER BY STU_CLASS ASC
SELECT STU_NUM, STU_PHONE FROM STUDENT WHERE  STU_TRANSFER >= 46
SELECT PROF_NUM, CRS_CREDIT FROM CLASS JOIN COURSE ON COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE WHERE CRS_CREDIT BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  CRS_CREDIT > 54

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT COURSE.CRS_CODE), CLASS_ROOM FROM CLASS JOIN COURSE ON COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE WHERE  PROF_NUM != 32 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM EMPLOYEE WHERE EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND CLASS.CLASS_CODE = EMP_NUM) GROUP BY CLASS_ROOM LIMIT 9
SELECT q.CLASS_CODE FROM ENROLL AS q WHERE  q.STU_NUM != 66 AND ENROLL_GRADE IN (SELECT ENROLL_GRADE FROM ENROLL AS d WHERE  d.STU_NUM >= 25) ORDER BY q.CLASS_CODE ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CLASS.CLASS_CODE), ENROLL_GRADE FROM EMPLOYEE JOIN CLASS JOIN ENROLL ON CLASS.PROF_NUM = EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM AND CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE WHERE  EMP_NUM = 72
SELECT DEPT_EXTENSION FROM STUDENT JOIN DEPARTMENT ON DEPARTMENT.DEPT_CODE = STUDENT.DEPT_CODE WHERE DEPT_ADDRESS IN (SELECT DEPT_ADDRESS FROM DEPARTMENT AS v)
SELECT k.DEPT_CODE, k.PROF_HIGH_DEGREE FROM PROFESSOR AS k WHERE  k.EMP_NUM < 66 ORDER BY k.DEPT_CODE DESC LIMIT 5
SELECT EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM FROM PROFESSOR JOIN EMPLOYEE JOIN CLASS ON CLASS.PROF_NUM = EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM AND EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM = PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM WHERE  PROF_NUM <= 79 ORDER BY EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT CRS_CREDIT), CLASS_TIME FROM CLASS JOIN COURSE ON COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE WHERE  CRS_CREDIT <= 71 GROUP BY CLASS_TIME HAVING COUNT(PROF_NUM) < 60 LIMIT 5

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT STU_INIT), STU_LNAME FROM STUDENT JOIN CLASS JOIN ENROLL JOIN COURSE ON CLASS.CLASS_CODE = ENROLL.CLASS_CODE AND COURSE.CRS_CODE = CLASS.CRS_CODE AND ENROLL.STU_NUM = STUDENT.STU_NUM WHERE  STU_GPA >= 75 LIMIT 4
SELECT PROF_HIGH_DEGREE, EMP_LNAME FROM EMPLOYEE JOIN PROFESSOR ON EMPLOYEE.EMP_NUM = PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM WHERE PROFESSOR.EMP_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT STU_HRS FROM STUDENT WHERE PROF_NUM BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY STU_HRS ASC
